<div>
<h1>Importance Of Traffic signal</h1>
<h2><strong>Traffic signals are designed to:  </strong></h2>
<p>
Ensure safe and orderly flow of traffic. <br>
Protect pedestrians and vehicles at busy intersections.<br>
Reduce the severity and frequency of accidents between vehicles entering intersections.
  </p>
</div>
  
