    <h2>Do you know the reason behind Zebra crossing</h2>
    <p>Zebra crossing is also known as a <b><em>pedestrian crossing</em></b> that is used in many countries worldwide and it is the oldest form of safe pedestrian crossing. Basically zebra crossings give the pedestrians some more rights.
</p>
